NK010(tha)001:0: phur pa rgyud lugs las chos 'byung ngo mtshar snang byed ces bya ba bzhugs /
NK010(tha)001:1: bcom ldan 'das phrin las kyi bdag nyid la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK010(tha)001:2: phur pa rgyud lugs kyi lo rgyus la sngon byung rgyud kyi lugs dang /
NK010(tha)001:3: phyis byung man ngag gi lugs so //
NK010(tha)001:5: 'di skad bdag gis thos pa'i dus gcig na /
NK010(tha)001:6: bcom ldan 'das zag pa med par mnyam par bzhag pa'i tshe /
NK010(tha)001:7: rdo rje 'dzin pas 'di skad ces bskul to //
NK010(tha)001:8: bde chen zhi ba chos nyid mchog /
NK010(tha)001:9: ston pa rdo rje chos nyid kyis //
NK010(tha)001:10: e ma ho 'dul bar 'gyur ba yin //
NK010(tha)001:11: de las longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku //
NK010(tha)001:12: 'jigs byed chen po'i skur bzhengs la //
NK010(tha)001:13: gdug pa'i tshogs rnams gdul du gsol //
NK010(tha)001:15: bcom ldan 'das 'jigs byed chen po'i skur bzhengs te /
NK010(tha)001:16: thun mong ma yin pa'i mtshan mchog gis mngon par spras pa'i sku des /
NK010(tha)001:17: 'og min gyi gnas lcang lo can gyi pho brang du /
NK010(tha)001:18: 'khor sems dpa' dang sems ma rnams la dam chos
NK010(tha)001:19: bdud rtsi phur pa'i chos rnams sku'i sgo nas 'jal
NK010(tha)001:20: bar bstan te / 'khor ba'i spong sgrib las kun
NK010(tha)001:21: rnam par spangs te grol ba'i sa la legs par
NK010(tha)001:22: bar bstan te / gnas so // thugs rje'i stobs kyis phyag na rdo rjes mngon par bsdus te /
NK010(tha)001:23: yang snying 'bru dgu'i tshul du thugs kar bstan /
NK010(tha)001:24: de nas sems dpa' rdo rje nyid kyis 'dod khams
NK010(tha)001:25: mthong ba'i lam du gyur pa rnams la de mngon
NK010(tha)001:26: par brtag par bya ba'i phyir phyag na rdo rje
NK010(tha)001:27: la bskul te / 'dod khams gnas rigs nyi shu'i ston par gshegs so //
NK010(tha)001:28: zhes pas mtshon te rgyud so so'i gleng gzhi la 'jug pa ltar ro //
NK010(tha)001:30: slob dpon chen po pra b+ha hasti dang /
NK010(tha)001:32: pad+ma sam+b+ha wa la sogs sangs rgyas kyi sa la
NK010(tha)001:33: bzhugs pa'i rig 'dzin rnams kyis rgyud las man ngag
NK010(tha)001:34: tu btus nas rnam par rig byed kyi bdag rkyen
NK010(tha)001:35: chos kyi rnam grangs bsam gyis mi khyab pa zhig
NK010(tha)001:36: las can so sor bka' babs pa'i don 'gog lam
NK010(tha)001:37: gyi bden pa'i 'bras bu'i ngo bo nyid du grub
NK010(tha)001:38: pa 'phags yul chos kyi gan mdzod nas gangs ri'i
NK010(tha)001:39: khrod du btsad po khri srong lde btsan gyi thugs
NK010(tha)001:40: bskyed la brten nas mngon sum du snang zhing /
NK010(tha)001:41: dngos grub thob pa'i brgyud pa zam ma chad la phur pa rgyal po lugs dang /
NK010(tha)001:43: lcam lugs gtso bor gyur pa'i bka' babs kyi nges pa tha dad mod /
NK010(tha)001:44: de dag las dang po ni /
NK010(tha)001:45: rgya gar gyi pan+di ta sh+r+ai dz+ny+aa na dang /
NK010(tha)001:47: lo ts+aa ba dpal gyi ye shes kyis bsgyur ba
NK010(tha)001:48: rdo rje bkod pa rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud le'u
NK010(tha)001:49: bco lnga pa mnga' bdag rgyal po'i thugs dam du
NK010(tha)001:50: bzhag pa nyid lugs srol 'di'i brten pa'i gtso bo'i
NK010(tha)001:51: mngon rtogs kyang de'i lugs sor bzhag dang /
NK010(tha)001:52: rten dang brten pa gzhan rnams ni ye shes rtse mo dang /
NK010(tha)001:53: rdo rje khros pa la sogs pa'i rgyud don sgrub thabs la 'jug che ba'i cha bsags shing /
NK010(tha)001:54: 'jug sgo dbang gis mtshon pa'i phrin las kyi rim
NK010(tha)001:55: pa ji snyed ni rtsa rgyud dang rnal 'byor chen
NK010(tha)001:56: po la sogs pa rgya che la don zab pa'i
NK010(tha)001:57: nang nas bsdu ba byas pa'i phyir na gtso bo'i
NK010(tha)001:58: mngon rtogs las phur pa rgyal po lugs kyi rtsa
NK010(tha)001:61: slob dpon chen po gshegs khar nyung la 'dus pa
NK010(tha)001:62: phur pa rtsa dum gyi don rdo rje khros pa
NK010(tha)001:63: rtsa bshad gnyis kyis bkral nas mkhar chen bza' la
NK010(tha)001:64: bstan pas / jo mos mon kha seng ge rdzong
NK010(tha)001:65: du dkyil 'khor rnam pa gsum la brten nas bsgrubs
NK010(tha)001:66: pas bdun gsum nas phur pa thams cad bzhad cing
NK010(tha)001:67: bstan pas / / 'phar g.yo dang 'od 'phro ba byung /
NK010(tha)001:68: pha mes kyi za 'dre la gdab pa'i phyir bsnyen
NK010(tha)001:69: phur dril bas nam mkha' la deng nge song nas
NK010(tha)001:70: za 'dre gnas pa'i rten dang brten pa tshar bcad
NK010(tha)001:71: / phur pa de jo mo'i dbon brgyud rnams kyis
NK010(tha)001:72: gdengs pas chog pa byung bas mkhar chen 'dre 'dul
NK010(tha)001:74: jo mos rang gi ming po dpal gyi gzhon nu la bshad /
NK010(tha)001:75: des lo rgyal ba'i blo gros /
NK010(tha)001:76: des mi nub rgyal ba'i snying po /
NK010(tha)001:79: des lag lhag rdo rje byang chub la bshad de bsgrubs kyang nus pa ma byung /
NK010(tha)001:80: de'i tshe khos chos la the tshom ma zos /
NK010(tha)001:81: rang nyid las 'phro zhan par rtogs pas rten 'brel
NK010(tha)001:82: ma log mkhar chen baza'i dngos slob a ts+aar sa
NK010(tha)001:83: le zhes bya ba phur pa gdengs pas gtsang chu
NK010(tha)001:84: yan man du chad cing tshe'i rig 'dzin thob pa
NK010(tha)001:85: de dang 'phrad par smon lam btab /
NK010(tha)001:86: de'i phyogs su mgo bstan nas nyal zhing bsgrubs pas
NK010(tha)001:87: a ts+aar sa le mu to bar bardzusa pa yar
NK010(tha)001:88: 'brog khor rer byung nas lag lhag la sgrub byas
NK010(tha)001:89: pas / a ts+aar sa ler dogs nas khyed rang 'dir bzhugs /
NK010(tha)001:90: da lta skya nam ngan pas zas mi rnyed byas
NK010(tha)001:91: te dbyar thog gro stabs chos zhu ba skad ma
NK010(tha)001:93: ston ser bon pa'i rnga gshang thos nas sgrub la 'gro tshad pa la /
NK010(tha)001:95: nga pha spun dgrar langs pa gcig yin pas /
NK010(tha)001:96: nga yi yul zhing ni khong tshos 'phrog na /
NK010(tha)001:98: de nas nga yang khyod dang sdong byas pas /
NK010(tha)001:100: de tshar gcod pa'i gdams ngag nga la yod zer nas phying khug nas be bum dang /
NK010(tha)001:101: phur pa bton nas man ngag ji lta ba bzhin byin no //
NK010(tha)001:102: der lag lhag gis bsgrubs pas shing sdong po bco lnga s+t+wa res bcad /
NK010(tha)001:103: gcig phyed tsam chod tsa na gnyid sad /
NK010(tha)001:104: rang gi ma la dgra la mthu rtags 'ong zhes smras /
NK010(tha)001:105: de'i tshe pha tshan rnams lag lhag gis mthu byas dogs nas gsod pa'i gros byed cing /
NK010(tha)001:106: ra bsad pa'i sha bsdu tshags byed tsa na khang pa rdib nas mi bco lnga shi /
NK010(tha)001:108: gshin rje'i mthu mkhan la 'jigs pa dge bshes ra
NK010(tha)001:109: lo ts+aa ba yang skrag par byas pas gshin rje
NK010(tha)001:110: mkhan po phur pa la rdugs zhes grags /
NK010(tha)001:111: de'i thugs kyi sras bzhi ni /
NK010(tha)001:115: sna nam shes rab tshul khrims bzhi las /
NK010(tha)001:116: nyang la yig chung can gyi lugs su gnang ba'i tshul ni /
NK010(tha)001:117: nyang gis slob dpon gyi jo mo dang mdza' bar
NK010(tha)001:118: byas pas mos jo bo'i thugs dam rtsa dum bya
NK010(tha)001:119: ba la byed / 'khor gyi sngags can de min
NK010(tha)001:120: byas pas khos slob dpon gyi dpe snod dom sgro'i
NK010(tha)001:121: zhabs brtol nas dpe brkus te bris pa slob dpon
NK010(tha)001:122: gyis mkhyen nas dam nyams bka' rkun khyod dang nga
NK010(tha)001:123: ba la byed / mi 'grogs gsungs / der nyang nad drag pos thebs pa la /
NK010(tha)001:124: bar pa btang gin bshags pa byed byas kyang ma gnang /
NK010(tha)001:126: da 'o na dben rtsi'i pha logs la dben rtsa brtsigs /
NK010(tha)001:127: sha khog brgya'i gtor ma thong /
NK010(tha)001:128: khrab brgya tham pas bshags pa gyis gsungs pa ltar byas pas nad las thar /
NK010(tha)001:129: da gdams ngag zhu byas pas /
NK010(tha)001:130: khyod dang 'phrad du mi rung gsungs nas yig chung byas kyin byin /
NK010(tha)001:131: de la dri ba dri lan mang du byung bas nyang gi yig chung can gyi lugs su grags /
NK010(tha)001:132: khos bka' brkus pas bkra mi shis pa yin skad /
NK010(tha)001:133: skrangs phur bu mgo la gnang tshul ni /
NK010(tha)001:135: bla mas slob ma btsal bas /
NK010(tha)001:136: kho mgo bo rgya mdud la sogs phur pa bsgrub pa'i mtshan dang ldan par gzigs nas /
NK010(tha)001:137: dkyus la gdams ngag mchan du btab nas gnang bas /
NK010(tha)001:138: skrangs mchan tika can gyi lugs zhes grags /
NK010(tha)001:140: rgan po blo rtul ba yin pas ma 'khrugs par bshad pas nor bu'i lugs su grags /
NK010(tha)001:141: kho rtog pa nyung bas phur tshugs su bsgrubs pas grub ste /
NK010(tha)001:142: dgra rnams gyang gi rtsa bar nyi ma 'de ba
NK010(tha)001:143: la phur pa 'phangs pas gyang 'gyel te thams cad
NK010(tha)001:144: shi bas de ltar du grags /
NK010(tha)001:147: bla ma'i thugs kyis kyang zin pas /
NK010(tha)001:148: gdams ngag thams cad zhal nas gsungs pas gsung sgros
NK010(tha)001:149: zin cing gnad la 'phog pa'i sna nam gdams ngag
NK010(tha)001:150: can gyi lugs zhes grags te /
NK010(tha)001:151: yig cha mdzad pa'ang shin tu dpyad bzod /
NK010(tha)001:152: rgyud lugs 'adi'ang rgyud kyi khog phub /
NK010(tha)001:153: man ngag sna nam lugs dang bstun pas gzhan la med pa'i gdams ngag go //
NK010(tha)001:154: spyir sna nam la lugs gnyis yod de /
NK010(tha)001:155: b+ha ti rgyas 'bring la brten pa kyi skor dang /
NK010(tha)001:156: zhal gdams rna brgyud la brten pa rin chen phreng ba'i lugs so //
NK010(tha)001:157: de ltar bzhi po la mi the ba'i spyang kir chung zhes pa las brgyud pa'ang yod do //
NK010(tha)001:158: yang phur pa lcam lugs su grags pa ni /
NK010(tha)001:159: cog ro bzas slob dpon dngos la thugs kyang /
NK010(tha)001:160: slob dpon gyis nam mkha' la dkyil 'khor sprul pa'i tshe /
NK010(tha)001:161: dbang yi dam la zhus pas yi dam slob dpon gyi thugs kar bsdus pas skal ba chad /
NK010(tha)001:162: slar jo mo mtsho rgyal la rjes su gnang nas
NK010(tha)001:163: jo mos cog ro bza' la gdams pa las brgyud
NK010(tha)001:164: pa'o // phur pa lha nag ni /
NK010(tha)001:165: o rgyan yab yum nas 'bre a ts+aa r+ya sa le /
NK010(tha)001:166: lag lhag nas rim par yar 'brog pa gu ru ba yang dag /
NK010(tha)001:167: 'dis rdzogs rim gtso bor 'don pa phur pa myang
NK010(tha)001:168: 'das kyi rgyud chen po la brten nas lha thams
NK010(tha)001:169: cad nag por mdzad pas lha nag tu grags la
NK010(tha)001:170: / gzhan rgyud sde phal cher mthun par lha khra shas che /
NK010(tha)001:171: des grub thob skor chung la bshad /
NK010(tha)001:174: rgya lam grags sogs la bshad pas bla ma rgya'i lugs zhes grags /
NK010(tha)001:184: rong lugs la sogs te brgyud tshul tha dad cing /
NK010(tha)001:185: de dag thams cad kyang mchog gi dngos grub thob pa /
NK010(tha)001:186: thun mong tsam du'ang dgra thul ba dang /
NK010(tha)001:188: lha ma srin bran du 'khol ba sogs mngon rtags gzhan las myur ba byung bas /
NK010(tha)001:189: gsar ma mkhan po ram la sogs pas kyang /
NK010(tha)001:190: dgyes rdor ram rje btsun ma chos zab kyang byin
NK010(tha)001:191: rlabs phur pa 'di las che ba med ces bsgrags
NK010(tha)001:192: shing / gsar ma dar gong du bod spyi'i yi
NK010(tha)001:193: dam yang phur kho na yin pas brgyud pa rabs
NK010(tha)001:194: su basngagasa 'os pa sha stag byung /
NK010(tha)001:195: khyad par phur pa 'di sangs rgyas thams cad kyi phrin las kyi bdag nyid yin pas /
NK010(tha)001:196: phur pa mkhan po tshe ring /
NK010(tha)001:198: mthu che zer ba ltar sngon byung dang bstun na
NK010(tha)001:199: slob dpon chen pos tsan+dana gyi nags la me shor
NK010(tha)001:200: ba la bsdigs pas nags tshal sngar bzhin gyur /
NK010(tha)001:201: bi ma las gang+g+aa gyen du log pa la gdengs pas klung chen yan man du chad /
NK010(tha)001:202: bal po sh+ai la many+dzusa brag mkhar gong can la gdengs pas brag ri dum bur song /
NK010(tha)001:203: jo mo mkhar chen bzas spyang ki'i rjes la btab pas spyang ki rbab tu shor /
NK010(tha)001:204: mi nub rgyal ba'i snying pos bya rog gis phreng
NK010(tha)001:205: ba khyer ba la bsdigs pas bya rog thang la
NK010(tha)001:206: lhung / lo dpal gyi blo gros kyis dmag gi
NK010(tha)001:207: spang khyim la btab pas mon dmag cham la phob
NK010(tha)001:208: lhung / / grub chen 'dar phyar gyis mu stegs
NK010(tha)001:209: 'phrog byed kyi grib ma la btab pas 'phur 'phror
NK010(tha)001:210: lhung / / sa la lhung / gnyags dz+ny+aa nas
NK010(tha)001:211: pha spun cham la phab pa sogs phyir dgra bgegs
NK010(tha)001:213: nang du rang rgyud kyi nyon mongs la thebs pas
NK010(tha)001:214: chos nyid kyi rtogs pa mngon du gyur pa brjod
NK010(tha)001:216: mdor na phur pa'i rgyud sde bod du phebs tsam
NK010(tha)001:217: nas bar chad gdon bgegs zhi ba bal yul yang
NK010(tha)001:218: le shod kyi lo rgyus sogs las yongs su grags
NK010(tha)001:219: pas mtshon / yul la mngon sum du snang ba'i mthu rtsal dang /
NK010(tha)001:220: yul can chos nyid du grol ba'i byin rlabs bsam
NK010(tha)001:221: gyis mi khyab pas rig 'dzin gyi slob dpon chen
NK010(tha)001:222: pos kyang thugs dam gyi ngo bo nyid du mdzad
NK010(tha)001:223: / spyir rdo rje phur pa'i rgyud sde'i ring lugs zab la byings che /
NK010(tha)001:224: rgya che la rnam grangs mang yang tshig don gnyis
NK010(tha)001:225: ka'i cha glegs bam gyi dbus na gter du gtams
NK010(tha)001:226: pa ltar bzhugs pa mngon du 'byung ba'i dus la
NK010(tha)001:227: bab pa na / phur pa rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud phyi ma las /
NK010(tha)001:228: 'di ni ko sa la yi gling //
NK010(tha)001:229: de ring rigs can de la 'bab //
NK010(tha)001:230: sprul pa 'jig rten mi gnas tshe //
NK010(tha)001:231: khyod kyi sprul pa pad+ma'i rgyal //
NK010(tha)001:232: de yi nus pa don byed 'gyur //
NK010(tha)001:233: zhes cig char ba'i rigs can bi ma la la sngon du babs shing /
NK010(tha)001:234: phyi nas bdag nyid kyi tshogs bdud rol pa'i snang
NK010(tha)001:235: cha la spa gro stag tshang yin rgyu ba'i phug
NK010(tha)001:236: pa kha shar lhor bstan pa zhig tu rlangs pa
NK010(tha)001:237: dpal seng gos dkar chas zhugs kyis rdo rje phur
NK010(tha)001:238: pa'i dbang bskur rdzogs par byin pa sogs lha dang
NK010(tha)001:239: bla ma'i byin rlabs kyi mtshan ma mang du thob
NK010(tha)001:240: pa'i tshe / bka'i bsdu ba gsar du byas shing /
NK010(tha)001:241: mngon rtogs dang dbang chog gnyis kyi bsdu ba zin
NK010(tha)001:242: tsam nas skya bdag po dbang sdud snying po'i mnal
NK010(tha)001:243: lam du da res phur khang du bla ma rdzogs
NK010(tha)001:244: chen po la yang dag gi dbang bskur zhus shig
NK010(tha)001:245: ces byung bas / yang dag pa'i chos tshul du
NK010(tha)001:246: nges pa rnyed nas dbang gi sgo 'phar dang por
NK010(tha)001:247: phye nas rim par spel bas byin rlabs kyi tshan
NK010(tha)001:249: bstan srid kyi bde thabs kyang rgya chen po 'grub
NK010(tha)001:250: pa yin pas yid bzhin gyi nor bu ltar gces
NK010(tha)001:252: ces pa'ang rig 'dzin 'jigs med gling pas gsang rgya
NK010(tha)001:253: grol nas yi ge snga ma las zhib tu bsnan
